title: Quarantine Check-In #2 👨‍⚕️🎷
description:
Justin and Christian react to their covid news making news. They give Jerry O’Connell a call and find out he’s teaching himself saxophone while stuck at home. Plus they call their doctor friend Dave Kessler to talk about his experience working on the frontlines in a NY hospital.
